metadata.description:
Re-entering with purpose, the 10-ENT Hoodie is a limited collection of 10 hoodies. 10 pieces have been re-released for this drop, and a Mixed Reality experience with AR interacting with the physical hoodie will be provided to experience all 10 Tenets.

*Note: Physical hoodie perk expires after redemption.
metadata.name: [SLST0103] Edition 1 of 10
